{Speech 2}{}{I'm sorry there is no place in the cattleshed. You should go somwere else.@@I am very busy right now.@@Smell? I think I just got used to that,@@It doesn't smell that bad here.@@I guess I won't have to fertilize the fields this year. Thank you.@@This one needs hay.@@Have to go bring more water.@@Yikes! Time to get a shovel.@@This one seems to be alright.@@I should look after this one. It seems to be falling ill.@@Zzzz... I'm sleeping... Zzzz...@@[Yawn] I had to get up early.@@Hey, I have a young and growing up organism. I have to sleep.@@Why don't you talk to somebody else?@@Oh my, how I want to sleep. I'll be happy if someone just stoped talking to me.}
